### Federation Monitor — all replications registered by the plugin
GET http://localhost:4005/pipeline/Pipelines

### Run history (most recent first)
GET http://localhost:4005/pipeline/PipelineRuns?$orderby=startTime desc&$top=20

### Status for a single replication (convenience function)
GET http://localhost:4005/pipeline/status(name='ExchangeRates')

### Trigger a named replication
POST http://localhost:4005/pipeline/run
Content-Type: application/json

{"name":"Categories","mode":"full"}

### Flush a cache entry (affects delegate entries, not replicated tables)
POST http://localhost:4005/pipeline/flush
Content-Type: application/json

{"name":"Carriers"}
